cales éthérées de Julien Pas se font plus enchanteresses que jamais. \n\n►  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wmd9BjnyLII\n► https://www.facebook.com/marsredskyband/\n► https://marsredsky.bandcamp.com/\n\n✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘ ✘\n\n? Où ?\n► La Maroquinerie\n► 23 Rue Boyer, 75020 Paris\n► Métro : Ménilmontant\n\n?Combien ?\n► 19.20€ (+ frais de loc.) en prévente ici : http://bit.ly/earthless_mrs_maroquinerie\n► 24€ sur place\n\n✘ Partenaires :\n► Heavy Report : heavyreport.com\n► The Unchained : theunchained.net\n► La Planète du Stoner Rock : laplanetedustoner.net\n► desert-rock.com : desert-rock.com',NULL,0,0,NULL,'\"{\\\"invited\\\": null, \\\"attending\\\": 154}\"','3f606cf5-7f37-4f67-9d15-2b45a9451ad2','2109545176025875',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-02-19 21:30:01','2019-11-06 22:10:29'),(149,6,'Father Befouled, Krypts, Encoffination, Jupiterian // Paris','father-befouled-krypts-encoffination-jupiterian-paris-gibus-live','2019-05-03 18:30:00','2019-05-03 22:30:00','Garmonbozia Inc., en accord avec Killtown Bookings, présente :\n\n? ? ?\n□ FATHER BEFOULED (death)\nwww.FatherBefouled.com\n□ KRYPTS (death) \nwww.kryptsdeath.com\n□ ENCOFFINATION (doom/death)\nfacebook.com/templeofencoffinment\n□ JUPITERIAN (sludge/doom/death)\nfacebook.com/jupiteriandoom\n\n?  Vendredi 03.05.2019 - Paris, Gibus Live\n\n► premier concert en France pour FATHER BEFOULED & ENCOFFINATION -  date unique en France ! ◄\n\n? -chers+jolis // 15€\n□ Envois postaux : billetterie@garmonbozia-inc.com\n□ Paris : Rock\'n Roll Voltage (+0.5€/ticket)\n\n? billetteries // 18.8€\n□ fnac bit.ly/FatherBefouled_fnac\n□ digitick bit.ly/FatherBefouled-digi\n□ ticketmaster bit.ly/FatherBefouled-tm\n\n_________________\n■ Garmonbozia Inc.?? ■\n? bit.ly/Garmon-events\n? bit.ly/Garmon-news',NULL,0,0,NULL,'\"{\\\"invited\\\": null, \\\"attending\\\": 51}\"','f9fd9dec-cfbc-4352-a1c1-f9fe86c65ced','212441932795303',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-02-16 16:41:58','2019-11-06 22:10:29'),(150,21,'Azz