e, et pourquoi pas un nouveau festival dès que possible.\n-\n\n[EN] The Fall of Summer is proud to announce two concerts of the italian horror maestro Claudio Simonetti\'s Goblin, to be held at Le Flow in Paris on Sunday the 31st of March. During the first show which will start at 3pm and be a seated concert, the italian master will perform its iconic score for the original Suspiria film in its entirety during film screening. The second show will start at 8pm, it will be a standing gig consisting of a selection of the best of Goblin\'s carrer like you had the occasion to see at Fall of Summer 2016 on the Blackwaters Stage.  \n\nIt\'s a joy for us to be able to make a new appointment with you and we thank you in advance for your support so we can carry on with this kind of events and maybe a new festival as soon as possible !\n\n----\n?️ Tickets : bit.ly/GoblinParisTickets\n? e-Shop : bit.ly/FoSShop\n----\n\n? FLOW Paris\n4 Port des Invalides\n75007 Paris \n? Métro : Invalides (Lignes 8 et 13)',NULL,0,0,NULL,'\"{\\\"invited\\\": null, \\\"attending\\\": 303}\"','4ea0aa6e-4895-455a-9357-5af2dad9c717','601468783634973',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-02-19 21:34:02','2019-11-06 22:10:29'),(273,13,'Týr, Heidevolk, Dalriada - \"The Tour From Hel\" // Paris','tyr-heidevolk-dalriada-the-tour-from-hel-paris-paris','2019-04-07 19:00:00','2019-04-07 22:30:00','Garmonbozia Inc., en accord avec RTN Touring, présente :\n\n? ? ? \"The Tour From Hel\"  ? ? ? \n□ TÝR (pagan folk)\nwww.facebook.com/tyrband\n□ HEIDEVOLK (pagan folk) \nwww.facebook.com/heidevolkofficial\n□ DALRIADA (pagan folk) \nwww.dalriada.hu\n\n?  Dimanche 07.04.2019 - Paris\n\n? -chers+jolis // 25€ // bientôt disponibles\n□ Envois postaux : billetterie@garmonbozia-inc.com\n□ Paris : Rock\'n Roll Voltage (+0.5€/ticket)\n\n? billetteries // 27.5€\n□ digitick bit.ly/Tyr-Paris-digi\n□ fnac bit.ly/Tyr-Paris-fnac\n□ ticketmaster bit.ly/Tyr-Paris-tm\n\n_________________\n■ Garmonbozia Inc.?? ■\n? bit.ly/Garmon-events\n? bit.l