l rendition by Till Lindemann with his unmistakable voice and all the intensity listeners have come to expect.\n\nThe starting point for these new LINDEMANN songs was a collaboration between Till Lindemann and Hamburg’s Thalia Theater for a modern adaptation of the fairytale of Hansel and Gretel, which touches on themes of fear, hope, poverty, excess, cannibalism, and death. Five songs from this critically acclaimed play are supplemented by six new compositions to form the impressive new studio album from LINDEMANN.\n\nThe first single, “Steh auf” (“Get Up”), which dropped in mid-September, is a hard-charging anthem that immediately shot into the top ten in the German singles charts. The music video was directed by star director Zoran Bihac, who also made earlier videos for Rammstein and LINDEMANN. Filming took place in Kazakhstan, with one of the protagonists played by Tägtgren’s fellow Swede, the Hollywood star Peter Stormare (Fargo). But that is only a taste of the new cycle. Fans are already eagerly awaiting the release of F & M and then, in February, will get their chance to experience LINDEMANN live at 12 European concerts.','https://la-scene-parisienne.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/covers/2020/lindemann-tour-2020-paris-france-sold-out-la-cigale.jpg',0,0,NULL,'{\"cover\": \"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/72756397_2787899137939119_1823576838241255424_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&_nc_ohc=P56Xgqkt_HoAQllNjyhNEBPIBDAMvMQgJIGRIW_WKLDUlBpulqJPe_enw&_nc_ht=scontent.xx&oh=1902b0d1462a0af2452336d0a7cbf837&oe=5E72A769\", \"invited\": null, \"attending\": 505, \"local_cover\": \"/2020/lindemann-tour-2020-paris-france-sold-out-la-cigale.jpg\"}','306c950b-2ca5-42fa-a538-dc645b750449','1179928195729475','{\"meta\": {\"rsvp\": {\"maybe\": 2435, \"invited\": null, \"noreply\": 202, \"declined\": 0, \"attending\": 1095}, \"cover\": \"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/72756397_2787899137939119_1823576838241255424_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&_nc_ohc=ItZovQuTqawAX--x-s8&_