 Hardcore Post Punk – Santa Rosa CA – US)\nSi tu n’étais pas déjà avec nous en juillet dernier, c’est l’occasion rêvée de (re)découvrir ce groupe qu’on ne présente plus et dont le dernier opus « Clairvoyant » figure dans la plupart des tops 2019.\n« We often think of hardcore as physical and not spiritual, but State Faults have found the place where all the hard angles meet the eternal circle. The Santa Rosa, California-based hard rock trio operate within the jagged maze of noise rock, mathcore, and heavy psych, bursting with agitated drums and yelped vocals that in still a sense of electric urgency. At the same time, their slower moments - and their album artwork - show a love of the creeping, doe-eyed spiritualism of cult worship. If you’re excited for Ari Aster’s Midsommar, you need to check these guys out. » - Kerrang!\n? https://nosleeprecords.bandcamp.com/album/clairvoyant\n\n? Boneflower (Screamo Alternatif – Madrid – SP)\nOn ne cache pas notre joie d’accueillir l’un de nos groupes favoris dans la scène ! « Without you I’m alone. »\n« Influenced by wide spectrum between the post-hardcore and post-rock music, Boneflower were born in Madrid (Spain) in 2015. They released their first Demo/EP \"I\'ll be the bones, You\'ll be the Soul\" in July 2015 and the next year, the labels Miss the Stars, Lifeisafunnything and Dingleberry co-edited the vinyl version. The second work was the LP \"Empty rooms, full bodies\", released in December 2017 co-edited by 8 labels. Following the 3 digital singles released in summer 2018, they recorded their second LP \"Armour\" in Summer 2019, which will be released in the spring 2020.Since the beginning, the band adopted a hard working DIY philosophy and toured heavily Spain and Europe non-stop.ng the weekends and Europe in summer tours. »\n? https://boneflower.bandcamp.com/album/empty-rooms-full-bodies\n\n? Plague Walker (Screamo Hardcore – Indiana – US)\nSide project de Shawn Decker (Coma Regalia), ce trio mixte délivre, depuis 2015 environ, des morceaux rageux à souhait, d’une minute en moyenne, à l’ancienne.\n? https://middlemanrecords.bandcamp.com/album/palomas\n\n? Komarov (Screamo Mosh – Leeds/Newcastle – UK)\n« Gratuitous blast beats and relatively tasteless breakdowns. » C’est clair, non ? Avec des membres de Cady et de Cavalcades\n? https://komarovband.bandcamp.com/album/komarov\n---------------------------\n⚠️ Pour info, nous ne tolérons aucune attitude violente, raciste, sexiste ou encore homophobe. Au moindre souci, n\'hésite pas à venir voir les personnes de l\'orga.\nEt aussi, on aime les chiens, les chats, les rats, les opossums... tant qu\'ils restent dehors (leurs petites oreilles te remercieront).\nCes règles permettent juste de garder les lieux cool ! On te remercie par avance d\'y faire attention... et, bien entendu, éclate toi ! ;)\n\n⚠️(??) FYI, we do not tolerate any violent, racist, sexist or homophobic attitude. At the slightest worry, do not hesitate to come and see the people of the association.\nAlso, we love dogs, cats, rats, opossums ... as long as they stay outside  (their little ears will thank you).\nThese rules just keep the place cool and safe for everyone! We thank you in advance to be careful of everyone... And, of course: have fun ! ;)\n---------------------------\nINFOS PRATIQUES:\n\n? PRIX LIBRE (mais nécessaire !)\n⏰ Start 20h\n\nLe Cirque Electrique\nPlace du Maquis du Vercors\n75020 Paris\n? 11 / Ⓣ 3bis arrêt Porte des Lilas','https://la-scene-parisienne.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/covers/2020/state-faults-boneflower-plague-walker-komarov-paris-le-cirque-electrique.jpg',0,0,NULL,'{\"rsvp\": {\"maybe\": 49, \"invited\": null, \"noreply\": 4, \"declined\": 0, \"attending\": 0}, \"cover\": \"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/84399695_505891430066994_7820923717013209088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&_nc_ohc=rgapeo29L20AX_yXKUl&_nc_ht=scontent.xx&oh=d13b6f0f9279a621660507d469e6bd7b&oe=5E961E69\", \"local_cover\": \"/2020/state-faults-boneflower-plague-walker-komaro