a-i-grift-i-solbrud-i-velnias-live-in-villingen-schwenningen-jugend-und-kulturzentrum-klosterhof','2020-04-25 18:00:00','2020-04-26 01:00:00','\"AMERICAN BLACK METAL TOUR PT.II: EUROPEAN ALLIANCE\"  \n\nUada - Black Metal, USA\nhttps://www.facebook.com/OfficialUADA/\n\nGrift - Black Metal, Schweden\nhttps://www.facebook.com/Griftofficial/\n\nSolbrud - Black Metal, Dänemark\nhttps://www.facebook.com/Solbrud/\n\nVelnias - Black Metal, USA\nhttps://www.facebook.com/VelniasCult/\n\nSamstag 25.04.2020\nEinlass 18:00 Uhr // Beginn 19:00 Uhr\n\nVVK: Euro 22,73\nOnline Vorverkauf bei Eventim, hier über diesen hübschen Link:\nhttps://www.eventim-light.com/de/a/5d0e6a5ba8e54a00010bdac2/\n\nLokaler Vorverkauf (Hardtickets): \nSoundservice, Färberstr. 14, 78050 Villingen-Schwenningen\n\nAK: Euro 26.- (nur falls Restkarten verfügbar sind!)\n\nÖrtlicher Veranstalter: \nBlack Forest Fest und Soundservice Villingen-Schwenningen in Zusammenarbeit mit dem Jugendförderungswerk Villingen-Schwenningen e.V.\n\n______________________________________________________\n\nUADA (US)\nFrom the darkness, UADA (meaning haunted in latin) emerges breathing the spirit of the original 90’s Black Metal wave. Since 2014, this Portland, Oregon four-piece has used a unique approach to combine raw black metal and spectral melodies.\n\nDevoid of Light: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UVZ2X39mxgU\nCult of a Dying Sun: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1WeeMHq3I3Y\n\nSPECIAL GUESTS:\n\nGrift (SWE)\nGrift is the one-man band by multi-instrumentalist Erik Gärdefors. Formed in 2011, inspired strongly by Swedish folklore, nature and existential questions. Grift\'s ambition is to capture the feeling of desolation and express this through music, words and images.\nGrift perform live, both as a full-scale band with four people, and alone with nothing but his voice and acoustic guitar.\n\nSvältorna: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ny7VIuPeAuI\n\nSolbrud (DK)\nFrom the birth of Solbrud (Danish for sun breach) in 2009, 